<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151278>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17–24. Gandhara (17–20) and Collita (21–24) spp.: adults. Depositories of the specimens: 17, 18, 22 and 23 in MWM/ZSM; 19 and 20 in NMNS (photos by S. Wu); 21 in NHMUK (©The Trustees of NHMUK); 24 in SZMN (photo by V.V. Dubatolov)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10151278/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151292>
    dc:description "FIGURES 47–50. Collita spp.: male (47–49) and female (50) genitalia. Depositories of the specimens dissected: 47, 48 and 50 in MWM/ZSM; 49 in SZMN (photo by V.V. Dubatolov)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10151292/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

